data.title: Unit I - Web Programming
data.meta_description: Unit I _Web Programming - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides an overview of web programming unit 1 and introduces some key concepts related to the internet and web technologies. It discusses what the internet is, how it evolved from ARPANET, and common applications and protocols used on the internet like email, FTP, HTTP, and browsers. It also summarizes advantages and disadvantages of using the internet and provides details on email components and protocols like SMTP.
